# ========================================
# DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS
# ========================================

# 1. LOCAL DEVELOPMENT:
#    - Copy this file to .env
#    - Fill in your API keys
#    - The system will automatically detect and use them

# 2. RENDER DEPLOYMENT:
#    - Go to your Render dashboard
#    - Navigate to Environment Variables
#    - Add each variable above with your actual API keys
#    - Redeploy your service

# 3. FREE TIER LIMITS:
#    - CryptoCompare: 100,000 calls/month (free)
#    - CoinGecko: 10,000 calls/month (free) 
#    - Alpha Vantage: 500 calls/day (free)
#    - Finnhub: 60 calls/minute (free)
#    - NewsAPI: 1,000 calls/day (free)
#    - MarketAux: 100 calls/month (free)

# 4. FALLBACK SYSTEM BENEFITS:
#    - Automatic failover between providers
#    - Rate limit management
#    - Cooldown periods for failed keys
#    - Always-on data availability
#    - Cost optimization across providers

# ========================================
# PRIORITY SYSTEM EXPLANATION
# ========================================

# The system tries providers in this order:
# 1. CryptoCompare (best for crypto data)
# 2. CoinGecko (excellent free tier) 
# 3. CoinAPI (premium data quality)
# 4. Alpha Vantage (comprehensive financial data)
# 5. Original RSS feeds (always available)

# Each provider's keys are tried sequentially
# Failed keys enter cooldown periods:
# - Rate limit: 5-60 minutes
# - Invalid key: 1 hour
# - API error: Immediate retry with next key

# ========================================